{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"041ed7c7e3","title":"接见共青团第三次全国代表大会代表时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6c7b9225bb","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":25,"articleId":"041ed7c7e3","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c58ee36bed","type":"title","text":"接见共青团第三次全国代表大会代表时的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"041ed7c7e3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6c2d6d602","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的会议开得很好。希望你们团结起来作为全国青年的领导核心。中国共产党是全中国人民的领导核心。没有这样一个核心，社会主义事业就不能胜利。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"041ed7c7e3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7c23fb5506","type":"paragraph","text":"你们这个会议是一个团结的会议，对全中国青年会有很大的影响。我对你们表示祝贺。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"041ed7c7e3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d56a5cf803","type":"paragraph","text":"同志们，团结起来。坚决地勇敢地为社会主义的伟大事业而奋斗。一切离开社会主义的言论行动是完全错误的。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"041ed7c7e3","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":417,"end":417}}}},"__N_SSG":true}